SUMMARY: 

The NOAA Office of Ocean and Coastal Resource Management (OCRM) announces its intent to evaluate the performance
of the Maryland and North Carolina Coastal Management Programs and the Chesapeake Bay (Virginia) National Estuarine
Research Reserve Program.



These evaluations will be conducted pursuant to section 312 of the Coastal Zone Management Act of 1972 (CZMA), as amended.
